overview: Compilation of Walt Disney cartoons, some featuring Donald Duck: CALIFORNY 'ER BUST; DON DONALD; THE LEGEND OF COYOTE ROCK; WIDE OPEN SPACES; A COWBOY NEEDS A HORSE; UP A TREE; GOOD SCOUTS; DONALD'S GOLD MINE; DUDE DUCK; PUEBLO PLUTO  Some variation of the contents occur in copies distributed in other countries; this list refers only to the print released in the UK.
title: Donald Duck Goes West
